{"tid":1810817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局啟動嚴重應變級別　限制探病時間","createTime":"2020-01-04T07:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:51:54.000Z","uid":10757,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"39622ed256f7639bd53183ec644b78f35a9462b7","tid":1810817,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局公布，因應政府就武漢不明病毒性肺炎病例啟動嚴重級別應變計劃，公立醫院即日起會啟動「嚴重應變級別」，在醫院及診所加強監察和感染控制的應變措施，包括限制探訪，當中一般急症病房將限制探病時間為每日不超於兩小時，每次不超過兩人探訪﹔療養及復康病房的探訪時間，則每日不多於4小時，每次不超過兩人探訪﹔至於隔離病房現已謝絕探訪，但恩恤原因會獲個別考慮。　　 發言人說，公立醫院會因應情況決定醫院義工服務及臨床實習安排，至於個人保護裝備的儲備，例如外科手術口罩及N95口罩等，相信可足夠使用3個月，醫管局同時會與供應商保持聯繫，確保保護裝備會有持續的供應，分佈7個聯網的隔離病床在有需要時會調動使用。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-04 15:15:48<br />\n<br />\n邊個仆街話冇事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68d3305b2fe911d768dc99668494227ab6340fa","tid":1810817,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"584b485ca62f26d19c6a7ba970440ea19ba55568","tid":1810817,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68d3305b2fe911d768dc99668494227ab6340fa","tid":1810817,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾期牆紙】 破局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=00b275a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aypmVes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn